.:: Puzzle 6x2-Level-1-2::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: handball, skateboarding
The people have 2 different hobbies: camping, filmmaking
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: action, crime
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: folk, pop
House: townhouse, farmhouse
The people use 2 different means of transport: motorbike, ship
1. the fan of pop is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is the fan of pop##1
3. the person watching action movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is camping##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the townhouse house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |
| Sport      | handball        | skateboarding   |
| Hobby         | filmmaking | camping |
| Movie-Genre   | action     | crime   |
| Music-Genre   | folk       | pop     |
| House           | farmhouse        | townhouse    |
| Transport     | motorbike  | ship    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 6x2-Level-1-3::.
