2 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, bongani
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: biathlon, parkour
1. the blend-smoker is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
2. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
3. the egyptian is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |
| House          | cape-cod    | palace      |
| Hobby         | writing   | baking       |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | martial-arts |
| Nationality   | egyptian  | colombian    |
| Cigar           | blend       | bongani   |
| Sport         | parkour   | biathlon     |

